I have some similar configuration errors that don't seem to prevent compilation. I assume they are Android or some other operating system what is bleeding through on the configuration:

Linux: Ubuntu 16.04
Compiling with GPU support
Commit: 91a70cb

Here is the full set of errors during ./configure:

INFO: Waiting for response from Bazel server (pid 4080)...
ERROR: /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/core/kernels/BUILD:2207:1: no such target '//tensorflow/core:android_proto_lib_no_rtti_lite_runtime': target 'android_proto_lib_no_rtti_lite_runtime' not declared in package 'tensorflow/core' defined by /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/core/BUILD and referenced by '//tensorflow/core/kernels:android_tensorflow_kernels_no_rtti_lite_runtime'.
ERROR: /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle/BUILD:213:1: no such target '//tensorflow/core:android_lib_lite': target 'android_lib_lite' not declared in package 'tensorflow/core' defined by /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/core/BUILD and referenced by '//tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle:signature'.
ERROR: /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle/BUILD:107:1: no such target '//tensorflow/core:meta_graph_portable_proto': target 'meta_graph_portable_proto' not declared in package 'tensorflow/core' defined by /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/core/BUILD and referenced by '//tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle:session_bundle'.
ERROR: /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle/BUILD:107:1: no such target '//tensorflow/core:meta_graph_portable_proto': target 'meta_graph_portable_proto' not declared in package 'tensorflow/core' defined by /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/core/BUILD and referenced by '//tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle:session_bundle'.
ERROR: /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle/BUILD:213:1: no such target '//tensorflow/core:meta_graph_portable_proto': target 'meta_graph_portable_proto' not declared in package 'tensorflow/core' defined by /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/core/BUILD and referenced by '//tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle:signature'.
ERROR: /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle/BUILD:213:1: no such target '//tensorflow/core:meta_graph_portable_proto': target 'meta_graph_portable_proto' not declared in package 'tensorflow/core' defined by /home/greg/tensorflow/tensorflow/core/BUILD and referenced by '//tensorflow/contrib/session_bundle:signature'.
ERROR: Evaluation of query "deps((//... union @bazel_tools//tools/jdk:toolchain))" failed: errors were encountered while computing transitive closure.
Configuration finished

I did compile the PIP package with no problems after getting these configuration errors.
